* Web based ERP interface prototype by Matteo Folin
* use Sproutcore 1.0 (and SCUI), all javascript, HTML and CSS

start debug server with ../abbot/bin/sc-server
build with ../abbot/bin/sc-build fweb -r
NB. git ignore tmp/**/*

